                    unßer &#x017F;tand Zur lincken, unßere &#x017F;toltze <rs type="person" corresp="#zeller2" resp="#MP"><choice><orig>am&#x0305;t menin</orig><reg resp="#MP">am&#x0305;tmenin</reg></choice></rs> will de<choice><orig>&#x02F7;</orig><reg resp="#MP">nn</reg></choice><lb/>
